headline: Equifax Releases 2024 Global Consumer Credit Trends Report
summary: Equifax® (NYSE: EFX) has released its 2024 Global Consumer Credit Trends, a report that features global consumer credit data and trends information from 10 different countries including Australia, Brazil, Canada, India, Spain and the United States.
